```
{{% /bs/toggle-item %}}

{{% bs/toggle-item "Windows PowerShell" %}}
```sh
$ENV:HUGO_MODULE_PROXY="https://goproxy.cn/,direct"
```
{{% /bs/toggle-item %}}

